# Build context is the repo root (backend image builds frontend + backend).
# Patterns are **-prefixed where they must match at ANY depth — dockerignore
# anchors bare names to the context root (backend/.venv, frontend/.env.local
# etc. must never reach the builder or the image).
.git
data
docs
go2rtc
**/.env
**/.env.*
**/.venv
**/node_modules
**/dist
**/__pycache__
**/*.pyc
README.md
CLAUDE.md
scripts
